<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="122" type="reference_group">
<paragraph pageId="1" pageNumber="122">
<taxonomicName authority="Warren, 1895" authorityName="Warren" authorityYear="1895" class="Insecta" family="Geometridae" genus="Orthobrachia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Orthobrachia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="122" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Orthobrachia</taxonomicName>
Warren, 1895. Novit. zool. 2: 121. Type species: 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Geometridae" genus="Stegania" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Stegania latifasciata" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="122" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="latifasciata">Stegania latifasciata</taxonomicName>
Moore, 1888 by original designation. In: Hewitson &amp; Moore, Descr. new Ind. lep. Insects Colln late Mr. Atkinson: 260. [Type specimen: Lectotype, male, Darjeeling in India (BMNH, London), designation by Yazaki in Haruta, 1992]
</paragraph>
